      <h2>Before you add or reduce zones</h2>
<p>There must be at least 1 month and 1 day remaining on your Travelcard at the date of change, not the date of your request.</p>
<p>You cannot change:</p>
<ul>
    <li>7 Day or monthly Travelcards</li>
    <li>Your Travelcard if you bought it from National Rail, Abellio or Trainline</li>
    <li>Your Travelcard if you paid for it using a warrant</li>
    <li>Your Travelcard if you previously reduced the zones on it<br />
    </li>
</ul>
<p>It will take up to 5 working days to process and issue you with a replacement card.</p>
